threads.title: A1989 820-00850-07
threads.message:
Hi,

I have an A1989 820-00850-07, that had a bit of liquid contact in the Keyboard conector area (J6700) and near QB631 area is a bit oxidated, with no power. It puls 5V from ampeter in all USB-C ports.
